## Add flake.nix to the project

{% steps %}

1. Initialize the template from the root directory of the project:

   ```shell
   nix flake init github:akirak/flake-templates#zig
   ```

2. Add `.envrc`:

   ```shell title=".envrc"
   use flake
   ```

3. Allow direnv:

   ```shell
   direnv allow
   ```

{% /steps %}
